               steal<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183004150125"></xptr>ing, on the <rs id="t18300415-274-cd1513" type="crimeDate">29th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-274-off1512 t18300415-274-cd1513"></join>, 2 pairs of trousers, value 7s.; 1 coat, value 5s.; 1 shirt, value 2s.; 1 hat, value 3s.; 2 waistcoats, value 2s.; 1 pair of stockings, value 1s.; 1 shawl, value 2s., the goods of 
